OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMorning mist and low cloud soon
OL,6,Fclearing. A warm day ahead, with light
OL,7,Fwinds and plenty of sunshine. The
OL,8,Fsunshine may turn hazy at times,
OL,9,Fespecially during the afternoon. A
OL,10,Flittle cooler along the coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine evening, then a clear
OL,13,Fnight for most. Some low cloud and fog
OL,14,Fmay develop along the coasts and over
OL,15,Fsome hills as the night progresses.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FAny low cloud and fog quickly
OL,18,Fclearing to leave a sunny day for all,
OL,19,Fwith light winds. Feeling very warm as
OL,20,Ftemperatures rise well above the
OL,21,Fseasonal average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
