OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure will keep it dry and settled,
OL,7,Fwith plenty of warm sunshine and winds
OL,8,Fremaining light. Some overnight fog
OL,9,Fpatches possible, mainly in the
OL,10,Fcountryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
